list.name: Changes
list.comment: Moved test suite to root package

task.summary: Documented PolymorphicDeserializer and updated serialized composite types in companion of StaticDeserializer.
Polymorphic write test is now passing.
Added Dokka packages and generated test binaries
Added proper variances to type parameters in Operations.kt.
Added fallback and static to local protocol test.
Simplified API. Some bugfixes and performance improvements. Updated README.md.
Package name now reflects GitHub Pages site.
Improved code style and documentation. Made all utilities internal aside from ReassignmentException.

Updated to 1.0.3
Changelog - Removed locally-defined protocols in favor of external read/write instantiation - All read/write sequences are now resolved lazily - Improved code quality - Removed ReassignmentException in favor of MalformedProtocolException - package 'io.github.aeckar.kanary.utils' is no longer exported by module 'kanary' - Converted write sequences from Set<WriteHandle> to Map<KClass<*>, WriteOperation> - Updated docs
Removed unused imports, cleaned up CollectionDeserializer, removed Container TODOs.
Made Type() pseudo-constructor internal instead of public
Removed local read() and write() in favor of direct implementation of read and write interfaces.
Changed JVM names for classes of static "of" functions
